title: ‘Ozark’ Season 4 Part 1, Episodes 1-4
description:
Joanna and Van give their thoughts on the first four episodes of this fourth and final season of ‘Ozark.’ Tune in next Tuesday for their reactions to episodes five through seven.
Hosts: Joanna Robinson and Van Lathan
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
